[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1105[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root‐cause analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The AddressSanitizer report shows that in cmsvirt.c [0m[1;39m([0m[39minside [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCreateNamedColorDevicelink [0m[35m/[0m[39m cmsTransform2DeviceLink[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the code is doing:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m WRONG: passing the address of the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte loop variable[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant,[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   but the downstream UnrollChunkyBytes routine unconditionally reads `nChan` bytes[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom that buffer. When `nChan` exceeds four [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor simply when it reads the byte at [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffset [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, it overruns the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte integer on the stack.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch strategy  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In src/cmsvirt.c, locate the loop that invokes `cmsDoTransform` with `&i`.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Replace the use of `&i` [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte `int`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with a stack buffer whose size [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatches the transform’s “bytes per channel” × “channels”:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Because the transform was configured with `[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, its input routine [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwill call _UnrollWordyBytes_ [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit per channel[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m rather than _UnrollChunkyBytes_. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Thus, declare a `cmsUInt16Number idx;` [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m so the input buffer is large [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menough.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Rewrite the loop as:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         cmsUInt16Number idx = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m i;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        &idx,[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant,[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. If in some configurations the input color space has more than one channel, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclare a small array:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cmsUInt16Number src[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mMAX_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m populate src[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m..nChan-[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, src, [0m[33m...[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ensuring the buffer size is always ≥ `nChan * [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mchannel[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Why this fixes the issue  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow came from UnrollChunkyBytes reading past the end of the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop counter. By supplying a [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor multi-channel[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m buffer that matches the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransform’s declared `[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnChan[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, the unpack routines [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnever read off the end of the stack.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This change preserves the existing color‐transform pipeline and does _not_ [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtouch any harness, fuzzing logic, or external libraries.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of functionality  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The only modification is the type and size of the input buffer passed into [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsDoTransform`. All other logic—profile creation, cached XFORM, LUT [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuilding—remains untouched.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The loop still iterates `nColors` times and stores results in the same [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`DeviceColorant` array.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side‐effects and mitigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Casting `i` into `cmsUInt16Number` truncates values ≥ [0m[1;36m65536[0m[39m. If it is possible[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto have more than [0m[1;36m65[0m[39m [0m[1;36m535[0m[39m named colors, switch to a [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte input buffer [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`cmsUInt32Number idx32`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and a transform built with `[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If the transform ever expects multi-channel input, the draft array approach [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`src[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mMAX_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m guarantees correct sizing.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verification  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After patching, rebuild the library and rerun the fuzzer under [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAddressSanitizer. The previous [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read past the end of the stack should no [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlonger occur.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All existing regression tests and harnesses remain unchanged, ensuring [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcoverage is preserved.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[12/24/25 20:38:11][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.ANALYZE                  ]8;id=584200;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=580196;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is an AddressSanitizer stack-buffer-overflow triggered during [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzing of the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer`. The overflow occurs when calling [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsDoTransform` inside `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, with the stack buffer overflow [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreported in `UnrollChunkyBytes` at `cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[39m`. A patch was attempted by [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchanging the loop index from a plain `int` to a `cmsUInt16Number` variable [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`idx`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhen invoking `cmsDoTransform`. After applying the patch, the same [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow error recurred, now attributed to the smaller `idx.i` [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariable space in the same stack frame of `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`. [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial AddressSanitizer log shows a one-byte read overflow at address [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;36m0x7fe432360d24[0m[39m`, flagged inside `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130:13[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow is traced back through `CachedXFORM`, `cmsDoTransform`, and [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CreateNamedColorDevicelink`, ultimately being invoked from [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink` in `cmsvirt.c`. The sanitizer indicates that a local [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack object named `i.i` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mat lines around [0m[1;36m1071[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m1185[0m[39m of `cmsvirt.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is only [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes wide [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and the read at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m overflows this buffer.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mKey observations from the initial issue:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash occurs on a single-byte read from unaddressable memory inside a stack [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mframe.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The immediate overflow site is within `UnrollChunkyBytes`, but the root buffer [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresides on the stack of `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The local variable `i` [0m[1;39m([0m[39man `int`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is passed by address to `cmsDoTransform`, which[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindirectly causes the overflow.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch attempt:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `src/cmsvirt.c`, the loop defining `i` was modified:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Original:[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Patched:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      cmsUInt16Number idx = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mi;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &idx, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This change reduces the size of the passed index to a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit stack object [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`idx.i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, with its bounds `[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m34[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, aiming to match the expected input type of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsDoTransform`.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mResult after patch:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The sanitizer report still shows a stack-buffer-overflow within [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow is now reported at offset [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m in the frame of [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, specifically overrunning the `idx.i` variable [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack frame still contains other local objects [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`dwFlags.addr`, `FrmIn`, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`FrmOut`, `LUT`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in close proximity, suggesting the overflow continues to target [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe same call sequence but with a smaller index slot.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for further investigation:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The implementation of `UnrollChunkyBytes` in `src/cmspack.c` and how it reads [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom its input pointers.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The data layout and expected size of the index parameter passed to [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsDoTransform` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpotential mismatch between caller and callee expectations[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The definition and use of local buffers within `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`cmspack` operations, allocation sizes, and object ordering[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to confirm correct [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack space reservation.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The code paths in `CachedXFORM` and `cmsDoTransform` that lead to processing of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchunky bytes and their assumptions about input pointer size.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1099[0m[39m:        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1105[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Identify and correct the input‐format channel count in [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCreateNamedColorDevicelink  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – In src/cmsvirt.c, locate the block where the “type” for the DeviceLink tag [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe formatter that precedes the cmsDoTransform loop[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is built. It currently reads, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor example:  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – This is wrong for named‐color device links: the input format must describe the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed‐color index [0m[1;39m([0m[39malways a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-channel value[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, not the device colorspace channels. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mChange it so that the CHANNELS_SH [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand corresponding COLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m refer to the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransform’s entry colorspace [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe named color input[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, not the exit colorspace. For [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexample:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt32Number InType  = [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                  | [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                  | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m   [0m[35m/[0m[39m* [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor the index *[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                  | [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[39m* ==[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt32Number OutType = [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                  | [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                  | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m                       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* same [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m-byte samples for device *[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                  | [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m[35m/[0m[39m* e.g. [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Then combine InType and OutType per the DeviceLink tag API [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtypically InType |[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mOutType << [0m[1;36m16[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and pass that to cmsWriteTag [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor cmsFormatterAlloc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m instead of [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe old single‐channel/exit workaround.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Ensure the temporary input buffer passed to cmsDoTransform matches the corrected[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minput format  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Once the input format is fixed to [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m channel × [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes, the old loop variable [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`i` [0m[1;39m([0m[39man `int`, [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m safely covers the [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte input slot and any pointer [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mincrements inside UnrollChunkyBytes.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Revert [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor omit[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m the prior attempt to use a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit `idx` variable; restore the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcall to use `&i` directly:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     This guarantees at least a [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte buffer, more than enough for the [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m-channel input.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Preserve existing functionality and test compatibility  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – By correcting only the channel count in the type tag and keeping the transform[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop logic intact, the pipeline semantics for named colors [0m[1;39m([0m[39mindex → device colors[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremain unchanged.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – The transform will now see exactly the buffer size it expects [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m × [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mso UnrollChunkyBytes can no longer overrun the stack redzone.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – All other paths [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnon–named‐color[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are unaffected since this change is made [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monly in CreateNamedColorDevicelink.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Verification  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Rebuild and re-run the cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer with AddressSanitizer.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Confirm that the stack-buffer-overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes is gone.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Run the full test suite to ensure no regressions in other color‐transform code[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpaths.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The sanitizer log shows UnrollChunkyBytes overrunning the input buffer because it[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwas told to expect more channels [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexit‐colorspace channels[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m than the caller [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mactually supplied.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By setting the input‐format CHANNELS_SH to the entry colorspace [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe named‐color [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindex, always [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, we align the expected buffer size with the actual allocation.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Restoring the use of the existing loop variable `i` [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m keeps a safety [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmargin greater than the required [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes and avoids introducing other buffer‐size [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmismatches.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No harness, fuzzer logic, or external utilities are modified—only the named‐color[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdevice‐link export path in cmsvirt.c is corrected.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This single change eliminates the root cause of the overflow without disrupting [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39many other part of the library.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The AddressSanitizer report pinpoints a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte stack overflow in [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunkyBytes.  This arises because the named-color branch in [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsTransform2DeviceLink invokes cmsChangeBuffersFormat with only [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX as InputFormat.  That constant lacks CHANNELS_SH and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBYTES_SH bits, so:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • [0m[1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m → [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • [0m[1;35mT_BYTES[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m → [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ⇒ PixelSize = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, Stride computed as zero, but UnrollChunkyBytes still loops [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnChan times [0m[1;39m([0m[39musing derived [0m[33mnChan[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m or spurious ExtraFirst logic[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, reading/writing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbeyond its local buffer.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key Insight from Existing Code[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the general device-link path [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot named-color[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, cmsTransform2DeviceLink [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomputes:[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       FrmIn  = [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mChansIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       FrmOut = [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mChansOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     and then calls:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, FrmIn, FrmOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By mirroring that pattern, UnrollChunkyBytes will see the correct [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes-per-sample [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and channels-per-pixel [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m for named-color indices[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meliminating the off-by-one access.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Strategy[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In src/cmsvirt.c, locate the CreateNamedColorDevicelink [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m1095[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhere cmsChangeBuffersFormat is invoked for TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace the existing three-line call that passes only TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mplus an output flags argument—and which in the last patch was incorrectly split [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minto four parameters—with a single three-argument call where:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • The second argument [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is the OR of:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         – TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         – [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         – [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m yields [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         – [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • The third argument [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Optionally [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand for clarity[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, you can introduce local variables:[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       cmsUInt32Number FrmIn  = TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                               | [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                               | [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                               | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       cmsUInt32Number FrmOut = [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                               | [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                               | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     then invoke:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, FrmIn, FrmOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure no extra arguments are passed to cmsChangeBuffersFormat, matching the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthree-parameter API.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By OR-ing in [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, UnrollChunkyBytes sees [0m[33mnChan[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand [0m[33mStride[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes per pixel, preventing it from reading/writing past its local [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This aligns the named-color path with the standard device-link path, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserving all existing color-space logic and not disrupting other transform code.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Removing the mistaken four-argument call restores API compliance and resolves [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe compile error.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Preservation of Existing Functionality[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness code, fuzzing macros, or test files are modified.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Other branches of cmsTransform2DeviceLink remain untouched, so all [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon–named-color transforms behave identically.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX still signals the transform type; we merely augment its[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformat bits so the buffer routines function correctly.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[3;35mNone[0m[39m anticipated beyond the intended fix: named-color indexing now correctly [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocesses exactly one [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit channel per named color.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If downstream code inspects or logs the format flags, it will now reflect [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [33mchannels[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, [0m[33mbytes[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m — which is accurate and consistent with other parts of the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcodebase.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Comprehensive sanity checks and existing libFuzzer/ASan runs should confirm [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat the overflow is eliminated and no new errors are introduced.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Validation[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild and rerun cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer under AddressSanitizer to verify [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe stack overflow is resolved.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run the full test suite to confirm no regressions in unrelated transforms.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mINFO:__main__:Running: docker run --privileged --shm-[0m[33msize[0m[39m=[0m[35m2g[0m[39m --platform linux/amd64[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--rm -i -e [0m[33mHELPER[0m[39m=[0m[3;92mTrue[0m[39m -e [0m[33mARCHITECTURE[0m[39m=[0m[35mx86_64[0m[39m -v [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/qqor/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95mlcms[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mout[0m[39m -v [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmp3t4j0x2i[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcms_virtual_profile_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is an AddressSanitizer–reported stack-buffer overflow in the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLittleCMS library during execution of the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer`. The [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow occurs in `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when invoked by [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink` in cmsvirt.c. A patch was proposed to change how buffer [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformats are set by replacing a single `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` call with separate [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`FrmIn` and `FrmOut` format masks. After applying the patch, the fuzzer run still [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtriggers the same [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read overflow at the same call stack, indicating that the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch did not eliminate the underlying buffer‐size mismatch.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m invokes [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink` in `src/cmsvirt.c`.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - During the named‐color device link creation, `UnrollChunkyBytes` in [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`src/cmspack.c` attempts to read one byte past a stack buffer.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - AddressSanitizer pinpoints the overflow at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m of a local stack variable[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the frame for `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Call stack:  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `CachedXFORM` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:537[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. `cmsDoTransform` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:206[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. `CreateNamedColorDevicelink` → `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1103[0m[39m+[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The local frame in `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` contains multiple stack objects; [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe overflow target is the object `[0m[32m'i.i'[0m[39m` at lines around [0m[1;36m1071[0m[39m in cmsvirt.c.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Original code in `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` used:  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The patch replaces that single call with two format masks, computed as:  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cmsUInt32Number FrmIn = TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cmsUInt32Number FrmOut = [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, FrmIn, FrmOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The rest of `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` remains unchanged, including the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation of local variables and the loop that feeds data through the pipeline.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Result After Patch  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Fuzzer output still reports the same stack-buffer overflow at [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes` invoked by `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow is again at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m in the stack frame, against the same local [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobject `[0m[32m'i.i'[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The sanitizer log and call chain are effectively identical to the initial run,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshowing that adjusting the format masks did not resolve the buffer-size mismatch.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **cmspack.c:UnrollChunkyBytes**: how it unpacks chunky pixel data and how much[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack space it expects.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **cmsTransform2DeviceLink frame layout**: the sizing and ordering of automatic[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariables—particularly `i.i`, `dwFlags`, `FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, and `LUT`.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **cmsChangeBuffersFormat**: whether it sets up internal buffers or LUT sizes [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly for named-color pipelines.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Pipeline configuration**: the number of channels, bytes per sample, and how [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minternal LUTs are sized and consumed by `UnrollChunkyBytes`.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Stack allocation patterns** around `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` to see if large[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLUTs or buffers are placed on the stack inadvertently.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis evaluation outlines the persistent overflow despite modifying format masks, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msuggesting a deeper mismatch between expected and actual buffer sizes in the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed‐color device‐link creation code.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+ [0m[33mFUZZER[0m[39m=[0m[35mcms_virtual_profile_fuzzer[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+ shift[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m961[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m IEEE [0m[1;36m754[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m2008[0m[39m [0m[32m"half"[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m962[0m[39m:#define TYPE_GRAY_HALF_FLT    [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPT_GRAY[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPT_RGB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m965[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m966[0m[39m:#define TYPE_RGBA_HALF_FLT    [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPT_RGB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m967[0m[39m:#define TYPE_ARGB_HALF_FLT    [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPT_RGB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mSWAPFIRST[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m968[0m[39m:#define TYPE_BGR_HALF_FLT     [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPT_RGB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mDOSWAP_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m975[0m[39m:typedef struct [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
