[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m25[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m26[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m27[0m[39m:#include [0m[32m"lcms2_internal.h"[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m28[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m29[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Generic I/O, tag dictionary management, profile struct[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m30[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m31[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m IOhandlers are abstractions used by littleCMS to read from whatever file, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream,[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m memory block or any storage. Each IOhandler provides implementations for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mread,[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m write, seek and tell functions. LittleCMS code deals with IO across those [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobjects.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m In this way, is easier to add support for new storage media.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m NULL stream, for taking care of used space [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-------------------------------------[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m NULL IOhandler basically does nothing but keep track on how many bytes have [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbeen[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m39[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m written. This is handy when creating profiles, where the file size is needed [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m header. Then, whole profile is serialized across NULL IOhandler and a second [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpass[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m writes the bytes to the pertinent IOhandler.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m:typedef struct [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number Pointer;         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Points to current location[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m45[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m FILENULL;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m46[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m47[0m[39m:static[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m48:c[0m[39mmsUInt32Number [0m[1;35mNULLRead[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsIOHANDLER* iohandler, void *Buffer, cmsUInt32Number [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize, cmsUInt32Number count[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m49[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m:    FILENULL* ResData = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mFILENULL*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m iohandler ->stream;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m51[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m52[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number len = size * count;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m53[0m[39m:    ResData -> Pointer += len;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m54[0m[39m:    return count;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m55[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m56[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsUNUSED_PARAMETER[0m[1;39m([0m[39mBuffer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m57[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m58[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m59[0m[39m:static[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m60:c[0m[39mmsBool  [0m[1;35mNULLSeek[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsIOHANDLER* iohandler, cmsUInt32Number offset[0m[1;39m)[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m61[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m62[0m[39m:    FILENULL* ResData = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mFILENULL*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m iohandler ->stream;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m63[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m64[0m[39m:    ResData ->Pointer = offset;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m65[0m[39m:    return TRUE;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m66[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m67[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m68[0m[39m:static[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m69:c[0m[39mmsUInt32Number [0m[1;35mNULLTell[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsIOHANDLER* iohandler[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m29[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This module handles all formats supported by lcms. There are two flavors, [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbits and[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m30[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m floating point. Floating point is supported only in a subset, those formats [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mholding[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m31[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m cmsFloat32Number [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes per component[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and double [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmarked as [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m bytes per [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomponent[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m as special case[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m ---------------------------------------------------------------------------[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This macro return words stored as big endian[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mCHANGE_ENDIAN[0m[1;39m([0m[39mw[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m    [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mREVERSE_FLAVOR_8[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m     [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0xff[0m[39m-[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mREVERSE_FLAVOR_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m    [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m-[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0xff00[0m[39m = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m255[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m257[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m255[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m256[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m = [0m[1;36m257[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m256[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m45:c[0m[39mmsINLINE cmsUInt16Number [0m[1;35mFomLabV2ToLabV4[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number x[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m53:c[0m[39mmsINLINE cmsUInt16Number [0m[1;35mFomLabV4ToLabV2[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number x[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m56[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m57[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m135[0m[39m:            v = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mv << [0m[1;36m16[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m alpha_factor[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m136[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mv > [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m v = [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m137[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m138[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m139[0m[39m:        wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mindex[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m v;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:438[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m446[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m438:c[0m[39mmsUInt8Number* [0m[1;35mUnroll2Bytes[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCMSREGISTER _cmsTRANSFORM* info,[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m439[0m[39m:                                     CMSREGISTER cmsUInt16Number wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m440[0m[39m:                                     CMSREGISTER cmsUInt8Number* accum,[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m441[0m[39m:                                     CMSREGISTER cmsUInt32Number Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m442[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m443[0m[39m:    wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m[1;35mFROM_8_TO_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*accum[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; accum++;     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m ch1[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m444[0m[39m:    wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m[1;35mFROM_8_TO_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*accum[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; accum++;     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m ch2[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m445[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m446[0m[39m:    return accum;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter reviewing the sanitizer report and the dispatch logic in cmspack.c, the root [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcause is that named‐color indexing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mTYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m currently falls through[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto the generic “UnrollChunkyBytes” routine, which only reads one byte at a time and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwalks the buffer by single‐byte increments. In our harness we pass the address of a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m-bit loop variable [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so UnrollChunkyBytes overruns that [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte stack [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mslot by reading past it. We need a dedicated unpacker that treats the incoming [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindex as a full [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit word and advances the pointer by two bytes.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix consists of two coordinated steps:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Introduce a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit unpacker for single-channel indices.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In src/cmspack.c, add a function along the lines of:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     static cmsUInt8Number*[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mUnrollNamedColorIndex16[0m[1;39m([0m[39m_cmsTRANSFORM* info,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                             cmsUInt16Number wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                             cmsUInt8Number* accum,[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                             cmsUInt32Number  Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m info and Stride unused for a single [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit word[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m info; [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Stride;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Read one [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index and store it.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = *[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m accum;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Advance by two bytes[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return accum + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Wire that unpacker into the [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit formatter table.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In the same file [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround the static cmsFormatters16[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m array[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, replace or insert [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe entry that matches TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX so that it uses [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollNamedColorIndex16 instead of UnrollChunkyBytes. For example:[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m* mask: match exact [0m[33mchannel[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, [0m[33mbytes[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m; ignore color-space bits, swaps, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39metc. *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m31[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m7[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mPLANAR_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mENDIAN16_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mDOSWAP_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mSWAP[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mFIRST_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mFLAVOR_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mPREMUL_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        UnrollNamedColorIndex16[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m,[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy doing this:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The fuzzer‐triggered path in CreateNamedColorDevicelink [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich does  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX, …[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   and then invokes [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, …[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will now unpack the index via our[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnew routine.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– That routine reads exactly two bytes from the buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madvances the pointer correctly. It will never read past the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte loop variable’s [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddress.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Other pipelines [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit chunky, planar, multi-channel, float[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remain routed to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtheir existing unpackers.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– No harness or test code is modified. All existing tests and the libfuzzer entry [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoint remain unchanged.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– This preserves the semantics of named‐color device link creation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwe still [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgenerate [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit indices[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and eliminates the [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte stack-buffer overflow reported [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby AddressSanitizer.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPotential side effects are localized to the named‐color‐index formatter dispatch. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWe should add a minimal regression test invoking cmsTransform2DeviceLink on a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone‐entry named‐color list to verify that the new unpacker is used and no overflow [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs. Once validated, this patch addresses the underlying mismatch between buffer[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize and unpacker logic without altering harness, fuzzing flags, or external [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdependencies.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[12/24/25 20:52:08][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.ANALYZE                  ]8;id=168935;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=703627;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\

[2;36m                    [0m         [39munpacking chunky bytes for a named-color path in `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`. A patch[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwas attempted by adding a special case in `UnrollChunkyBytes` to handle [0m            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame call site in `UnrollChunkyBytes`.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. UnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Special-case named-color index: unpack as a single [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit word and advance [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby two bytes[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo -> InputFormat == TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = *[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m accum;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        return accum + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cmsUInt32Number nChan      = [0m[1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo -> InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cmsUInt32Number DoSwap     = [0m[1;35mT_DOSWAP[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo ->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cmsUInt32Number Reverse    = [0m[1;35mT_FLAVOR[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo ->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The intent was to intercept the named-color branch early and consume exactly two [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line numbers shifted from [0m[1;36m130[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m136[0m[39m after insertion.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mResult of Patch  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Re-running the same fuzzer command yields an identical AddressSanitizer error at [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:136[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mshifted location of `UnrollChunkyBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow still occurs when unpacking chunky bytes in the named-color [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransform path.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack frame details [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i` buffer, its boundaries, and the overflow offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremain unchanged.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The logic in `UnrollChunkyBytes` beyond the named-color special case: how [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Stride`, `nChan`, and buffer pointers `wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` are handled.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Bounds and size of the stack-allocated buffer `i.i` in `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and how many bytes `UnrollChunkyBytes` can read/write.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Upstream callers’ expectations of input buffer size and alignment for the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed-color index format.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Other packing/unpacking routines in `cmspack.c` that might compute an incorrect [0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m136[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mv > [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m v = [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m137[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m138[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m139[0m[39m:        wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mindex[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m v;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The one-byte stack-buffer overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes occurs because, for [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed-color device links, the input pixel format consumes two bytes per index [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalue, but the default byte‐by‐byte unpack loop in UnrollChunkyBytes only advances [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe input pointer by one byte per channel.  Over multiple channels or on the final [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchannel this reads past the end of the stack buffer `i.i` in [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsTransform2DeviceLink.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A prior patch tried to detect named‐color inputs by testing for exact equality[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39magainst `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX`.  However, the transform’s `info->InputFormat` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moften includes additional flag bits [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcolor‐space, float, swap, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so the strict[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mequality check never fires; UnrollChunkyBytes falls back to the [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit path.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy to Fix[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Broaden the named‐color detection to a masked test on the format’s “[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone-channel” signature, rather than exact equality.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Mask off only the channel‐count and byte‐count fields from [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`info->InputFormat` and compare to `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX`.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - That pattern correctly matches “[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m channel of [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte data” irrespective of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother bitfields.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. When the masked test passes:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Read exactly two bytes from `accum` into a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index, handling system [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mendianness via a small manual shift or a byte‐swap if required.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Store the resulting cmsUInt16Number into `wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Advance `accum` by the full pixel stride [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Stride`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, not merely [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  This guarantees pointer consistency even if stride [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdiffers [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. padded pixels[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. Leave the remainder of UnrollChunkyBytes untouched so all other formats [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit chunky, planar, floating, premultiplied, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m continue to work as before.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Implementation Steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `src/cmspack.c`, locate `UnrollChunkyBytes` near line [0m[1;36m96[0m[39m.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add at the top:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Define a mask for Channels + Bytes fields[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     #define NAMED_INDEX_MASK [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Special‐case named‐color: [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m channel, [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes per sample[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo->InputFormat & NAMED_INDEX_MASK[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Load [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index from accum, big‐endian order by convention.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         cmsUInt16Number idx = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39maccum[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m << [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | accum[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = idx;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Skip the entire pixel stride[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return accum + Stride;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove or replace the previous `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo->InputFormat == [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` block.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure `NAMED_INDEX_MASK` and `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` are available via the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting include [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`lcms2.h`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Why This Works[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By masking only the `CHANNELS_SH` and `BYTES_SH` bits we correctly identify [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe “named‐color index” format regardless of any auxiliary bits set by [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsChangeBuffersFormat`.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Reading two bytes and advancing by the full `Stride` prevents the one‐byte [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mundershoot that caused the overflow.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All other code paths in `UnrollChunkyBytes` remain unmodified, preserving [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting unpack logic for [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit chunky, floating data, swapping, premultiplication,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand so on.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side Effects & Mitigation[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This patch captures any “[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-channel, [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte, non-floating” format.  In ordinary[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39musage that includes only named‐color device‐links, so no unintended formats should [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe affected.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If the library ever supports raw [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit grayscale input via [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`, that code would now also take the masked branch; however, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgrayscale [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit is typically handled in a separate unpacker [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. UnrollChunky16[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIf we later add genuine [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit chunky formats, we can refine the mask to test an [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexplicit “named‐color” flag in the transform.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No fuzzing harness, utility function, or external library code is modified.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verification[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild and re-run `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer`; the ASan overflow at [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmspack.c should disappear.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run existing unit tests [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif any[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for other chunky formats to confirm no [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregressions.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
